SUMMARY:Meeting Shaw re: AI
DESCRIPTION:<2018-05-25 Fri 10:30>\n• Watkins will pitch idea to Army and S
 eiksiu\, already discussing\n  percentages\n• Hsu will prepare three slide
 s for him\n• HB asked if Hsu had talked with Bradley or Katsumata\, and Hs
 u said\n  no\n• Hsu said when money starts coming in that people will get 
 interested
